          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-navy-900 mb-2">Courtage énergie</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-navy-600 leading-relaxed">Négociation de contrats électricité et gaz pour les professionnels. Économies garanties.</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/mobilite-electrique/" class="group block bg-white rounded-lg p-8 border border-navy-100 hover:border-gold-300 hover:shadow-lg transition-all no-underline">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-md bg-navy-100 flex items-center justify-center mb-5 group-hover:bg-gold-100 transition-colors">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-navy-700 group-hover:text-gold-700" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="m3.75 13.5 10.5-11.25L12 10.5h8.25L9.75 21.75 12 13.5H3.75Z" /></svg>
          </div>
